  "instructions": [
    "preheat a non-stick skillet over medium heat",
    "add the quinoa flour and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly",
    "add the parmesan cheese and cook for an additional 2 minutes, stirring constantly",
    "in a separate bowl, whisk together the egg, salt, and black pepper",
    "add the anchovy fillet, bonito-shave, onion, and garlic to the egg mixture and mix well",
    "add the egg mixture to the quinoa flour mixture and mix until just combined",
    "form the mixture into 4-6 patties, depending on desired size",
    "add the patties to the skillet and cook for 3-4 minutes on each side, until golden brown and crispy",
    "serve the patties on a toasted bun with your favorite toppings"
